\subsection{Nonequilibrium dynamics}
The nonequilibrium dynamics has been studied by means of the time-convolutionless projection operator method described in Ref.~\cite{DeLiberato2009}. Due to the anharmonicity introduced by the polariton, it implies that the baths will have a coloured nature. Under this description the master equation that governs the dynamics reads ($\hbar=1$)
